@keyframes personalLoaderLoading {
    0% {
    background-position: 200% 50%;
    }
    100% {
    background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
}
#personal-loader .loading {
    background: #9d88d3;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0px 2px 1px #0003;
    margin: 10px 7px
    position: fixed;
    z-index: 99999;
    height: 25px;
    aspect-ratio: 10/1;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4d27ad, #2c253d);
    background-size: 200% 100%;
    animation: personalLoaderLoading 1.5s infinite;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 600;
}

  "background": {
    "service_worker": "background.js"
  },
